    {
      "instruction": "<p>Reboil a kettle</p><p>Peel and finely slice your <strong>shallot[s]</strong></p><p>Peel lengths off your <strong>courgette[s]<span class=\"text-danger\"> </span></strong>with a peeler until you end up with a pile of courgette ribbons</p>",
