        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Dissolve your <strong>creamed</strong> <strong>coconut </strong>and<strong> rice vinegar </strong>in 500ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[750ml]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[1L] </span><strong>boiled water</strong> with your <strong>chicken stock mix</strong>, <strong>soy sauce</strong>, <strong>fish sauce</strong>, <strong>lime leaves</strong> and 1 tsp<span class=\"text-danger\"> <span class=\"text-purple\">[1 1/2 tsp]</span> [2 tsp]</span> <strong>sugar </strong>– this is your <strong>coconut stock</strong></p><p>Chop your <strong>chicken breast strips </strong>into smaller strips</p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-3-1692111819276-x200.jpg",
