            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once done, transfer the <strong>cooked chicken</strong> to a clean board and shred it apart, using two forks - this technique is known as ‘pulling’</p><p>Return the <strong>pulled chicken</strong> to the pan and give everything a good mix up – this is your <strong>Thai-style chicken & turmeric soup</strong></p>",
      "order": 7,
      "media": {
