    {
      "instruction": "<p>Discard the <strong>lime leaf[ves]</strong></p><p>Add the <strong>drained rice noodles</strong> to a bowl and top with the <strong>Thai-style chicken & turmeric soup</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
